{
  "stem": "33.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because there we were, some spoiled little brats who never even had a broom in our hands or never did anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we decided to clean some of these people's houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because we thought that it's dirty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I can still see them, sort of in a corner and looking at us like, you know, what are you doing in my house?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we thought that we're doing good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, we were too young, I think, to realize that it wasn't our business if their house wasn't as spotlessly clean as we were used to houses to be.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But basically, we had still a good life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it wasn't totally carefree, because things started to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like there was-- I think the first year, maybe 1941, there was an article in our local newspaper where they were ridiculing Jews who went to the beach by the river.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was sort of a very nice area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- everybody who went there, we all had like little cottages-- not to sleep in, but just to keep things for the summer and to get dressed there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had like little patios with benches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, especially us youngsters, we spent a lot of time during summer there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And our parents came out in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the women were playing cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was like really a nice place to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the first year this article appeared about Jews throwing goose bones on the-- on the-- you know, streets of this little park-- and so we boycotted the place for the first year.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our parents decided that we're not going to go anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were stupid, because they needed us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
